{
  "id": "RAW_de886680",
  "title": "不只 OpenClaw，这个 app 让你同时拥有龙虾和云手机",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&mid=2247488951&idx=1&sn=47b70ae43a8b976399fca297aa5ef0e5",
  "date": "2026-03-17 07:58:00",
  "author": "花叔",
  "siteName": "花叔",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed75678c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaNEfzwzDSW8WHqINCnDh9FxllxCbTQzffLxY2a7dauMlccDJX3Xd9HkWpwZVMYD9V3sibLSTUlIFeIcUL8GSicQVLpqUFIocj6cIWNL7xcIkc%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #fff !important;padding: 16px 12px 36px 12px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">上周五，我应B站邀请，去做了他们OpenClaw主题直播的嘉宾之一。本来想挑战5个OpenClaw完成工作的实战任务，还战战兢兢给直播起了个「会翻车吗？」的疑问句标题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然最后拿OpenClaw开发出了个app。但过程其实是……特么直播一开始就翻车了。当时我的本地OpenClaw因为上下文长度超限，一直卡在压缩上下文的环节出不来。于是我在这次直播中做的第一件事，就是用Claude Code去修OpenClaw。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 500px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100005278\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c070348&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaNEfzwzDSW8LdCp5V8cXFF9LwGZKIYiayiajRWZSNicJabsvxA2wCRODfKvACr0licibzNRmy0GyZxE0qbibicAiciavutyWkfmqSn0ndQtqFAHcYZJ4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过那次直播，我算是真懂了：对大多数人来说，要配置一个属于自己的OpenClaw有多困难，要踩多少坑。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，我都在公众号里写过这么多OpenClaw的内容了，你总该体验过了吧？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么？还没有？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">那好吧，我发现了一个完完全全不需要折腾，能免费体验，甚至都不需要打开电脑的OpenClaw使用方式。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">那就是「RedClaw」app。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它在云端帮你把OpenClaw的环境全部搭好，你只需要打开一个App，用聊天的方式下指令，龙虾就在后台帮你干活了。不用配API Key，不用装Docker，不用上下文爆炸之后手忙脚乱去修。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.172222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005279\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6708f84d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FaNEfzwzDSW86dyVgjrX8Be9ePNBbh7iclHK8ZKnuVYfjbYs1PgkVhibG72RSVuXmXoufibqaYEB7M9370j9ADFEDIlxFFtNzEQFG86uN2OC3cg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=88b882c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSWibdw5x2umKztJn9R8icVCKxamriaicMs7hhkEwen9PHZibN6CbxH89H6FPrCgDhx1DtjVich9cYFGF4MRJh2ttBYg5HFDnicg9b5awFc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005281\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95667c5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSW9HU61mA7UI7SHMQZfxH3ub5bJFTDtj57UtWg37QvfGqNIeQrzEKhacU1nZML8QPkkxiaGIkhricyjEnvd4UhibZUoXEK22rjboQM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，你一次性得到了两个东西：一台独立隔离的云手机，加上一个能自动操控这台云手机去执行任务的AI。云手机提供真实的Android环境，RedClaw的AI负责理解你的指令、拆解步骤、控制云手机里的App去干活。这两件事自己搭起来，正常人得折腾一个下午。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而云手机里还预装了OpenClaw——它在这里的身份就是个App，和抖音、淘宝平级。你可以接管云手机直接用它，或者让RedClaw去帮你操控它完成一些PC端才能干的任务，算是个隐藏彩蛋，后面会提到。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前RedClaw在各大安卓应用市场都可以直接搜索下载，iOS版本则需要再等一等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6907407407407408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 500px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100005298\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8c94a89&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSW8vIiabJRuEUEvmpDU878iaWAve0ibDa3BU6qFDIBUa0cmfn4nIvJicYAyia1fpw3SZs95LmZBkdWkBG8ME5iaKRdCGP5bbGjshtT2VA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我第一次打开的时候，我有种，我去...还能这样？的感觉</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">尝试了几天后，我发现它真正有意思的地方，还不只是「零门槛体验OpenClaw」这一点。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 32px 0 16px;padding: 12px 20px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">龙虾有一个盲区</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">先说我自己的体验。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">桌面端的OpenClaw（加上Claude Code）现在能帮我干很多事：写代码、跑自动化脚本、接飞书钉钉、搜网页信息，基本能覆盖了我电脑上80%的重复劳动。但有一类任务它一直处理得很勉强，甚至根本干不了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如我想看看抖音上最近关于某个话题有哪些热门视频，让PC端的龙虾去查，它要么给你搜出来的是抖音的网页版（内容残缺，推荐算法完全不同），要么压根绕不进去。再比如我想知道小红书里用户对某个产品的真实评价，想看TapTap上哪些独立游戏最近口碑在涨……</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些需求有个共同点：数据不在网页上，在App里。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国互联网有一个很特殊的格局，和欧美完全不一样。我们大量的内容和服务是App原生的，刻意不提供Web入口，或者Web版本是被阉割过的。抖音、小红书的推荐流你在网页上看不到。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就是所谓的「移动端数据孤岛」。桌面端的龙虾撞上了这些孤岛，基本就失效了。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 32px 0 16px;padding: 12px 20px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">云手机是进入孤岛的钥匙</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">RedClaw做的事情，本质上是一套「帮你把龙虾送进移动端孤岛」的基础设施。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">逻辑很简单：你在RedClaw的聊天框里下指令，它的AI理解任务之后，去操控云端一台真实的Android手机——打开App、点按钮、看屏幕、滚动页面，就像一个人坐在那台手机前操作一样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 500px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100005277\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d5551c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSW86TlnJEO8Mcqt9TqXZeh8F7I11mnFoibjWnlicVfcYw75y8oxBsIpGGjVTm8KNIQiakJDicIYhnbRKnU7EaqWfT2gtic8FicQMe6Kto%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">用人话说：你不是在让AI操控你自己的手机，而是在让AI操控一台「替身手机」，这台替身手机装了和真机一样的App，能进入那些只有移动端才能进的地方。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里有一个设计细节我觉得做对了：你的真实手机和这台云手机是物理隔离的。你银行卡绑定信息、聊天记录、通讯录，龙虾根本看不到，也摸不到。遇到需要输入验证码或者支付密码的步骤，系统会暂停并推给你一个「接管手机」的按钮，你自己来操作那几秒钟，操作完AI接着干。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005283\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=932bc1c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FaNEfzwzDSW96icrYdsaEMUHj1aVszibwbm8FQbQ3B9xrEbzW8OLWcmnb0pyu8YGhB0qzu6Fqic2LzgTclZP8CuGel0knicUywsYFVsib0Qt0L8wU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100005282\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f372ac84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FaNEfzwzDSWicZYaV0KVwIX9ZT8E913srxbK5O35zBTD4ibDQx7uKukAD2AlBbpj5J8jXsvwmETm0p1YfD6lxZh96HOnciaBjWm9AxQNLguP4po%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个隔离逻辑比那些直接要求在你真机上授最高权限的方案稳健很多。一旦AI跑在你自己手机里，有个问题始终没有清晰的答案：它的边界在哪里？云手机这个架构，至少在心理层面把这个问题解决了。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 32px 0 16px;padding: 12px 20px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">先做这件事：给云手机装好App</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在聊测试结果之前，有一件事得先说清楚，因为很多人上来就问AI干活，反而跳过了这一步。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">RedClaw的云手机是一台空手机，默认只预装了少数几个App。想让AI帮你操作抖音，得先在云手机里装好抖音。想让它查淘宝，得先装淘宝。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">云手机里有应用市场，但直接在那个界面手动操作很麻烦。我做的第一件事是直接告诉RedClaw：「帮我在云手机里下载美团」。AI会自己去找应用市场、搜索、安装。这个动作本身就是一个很好的热身任务——简单、成功率高，同时帮你把后续需要的App装好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100005301\" data-ratio=\"0.6490872210953347\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"986\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24297d59&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FaNEfzwzDSWibg23TIj2ATCiaIhrYP6W1Xzc37B78aRJwYfaTw4NODEGcp0gHS7PzHsXEMwdbuu8mico1FLiamooVichVXpR1NWayIsNgIR7YIrpg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这台云手机的完整度直接决定了你后面能外包多少任务给它。我现在装好了：百度贴吧、淘宝、微博、抖音、快手、TapTap等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 18px 0 !important;line-height: 1.85 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100005286\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" style=\"max-height: 500px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/